[SYNOPSIS]
.TP 5
\fBlcm-logger \fI[options]\fR \fI[FILE]\fR

[SIGNALS]
.PP
On platforms defining SIGHUP, lcm-logger will react to HUP by closing the
active log file and opening a new one.

